- [ ] Alt+S cycles modes correctly
- [ ] Status bar updates on mode change
- [ ] Mode persists across sessions
- [ ] F1 help documents Alt+S
- [ ] Graceful handling when semantic unavailable
- [ ] Works in common terminals (iTerm2, Terminal.app, gnome-terminal, Windows Terminal)

## Depends On
- hyb.search (SearchMode enum)

